"for the focuser to move to the requested position before declaring a "
"timeout. This should only be triggered if there are problems with the "
"focuser during the Focus process so set this to a high enough value that it "
"will not occur during normal operation."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Tempo-Limite do Movimento</guilabel>: A quantidade de tempo em "
