#. Tag: para
#: ekos-focus.docbook:2295
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<emphasis role=\"bold\">Backlash Managed by Device Driver</emphasis>: If "
#| "your device driver has the ability to manage backlash then you can use "
#| "this facility and turn off AF Overscan (set to zero). Alternatively, you "
